<p>From <a href="https://twitter.com/saruspete">@saruspete</a>'s <a href="https://twitter.com/saruspete/status/1014801074794979335?s=12">tweet</a>, ${PIPESTATUS[@]} gives ya all piped commands' return codes:</p>
<pre><code class="language-{.bash">echo foo | grep bar | tr z a | cat
echo ${PIPESTATUS[@]}
</code></pre>
